public class DropTargetEvent
extends java.util.EventObject

Event information about the drop target from the DropListener. example : dropWidget.addDropListener(new DropListener() { public void onDragEnter(DragSourceEvent event) { Widget myWidget = (Widget) DragSourceEvent.getObjectEvent(); } .... });
